ys.  Looks more to me like someone's friend got their feelings hurt and so they came here to do some name calling to make themselves feel better over it.  Then a lot of people jump on the &quot;anti-uber&quot; band wagon based on heresay and we are left with what we have here.  Leave your spite and jealousy behind and look at the facts.  You will see a lot different picture than the one you are painting.<br>
